c: 35
v: 32
t: "Sabe sesibanikeza incwadi njengendlalifa labo esabakhethayo ezincekwini zethu, ngakho-ke phakathi kwabo kunalowo owona umphefumulo wakhe futhi phakathi kwabo kunalowo omaphakathi nendawo futhi phakathi kwabo kunalowo ophambili kunabo bonke ezenzweni ezinhle ngemvume kaMvelinqangi lokho kungumusa omkhulu"